    <p>Losing your smartphone can be a major headache, especially if you depend on your device to keep in touch with friends &amp; family, stay on top of your workload and keep track of your daily schedule, to-do list and other important tasks. We know how it is.</p>
    <p>As a high-end, flagship phone, the Galaxy S9+ is a major target for theft. That's why our mobile insurance covers your Samsung Galaxy S9 Plus for theft, loss and even accidental damage, meaning you'll be insured if your phone goes missing or breaks after it's dropped or otherwise damaged.</p>
    <p>We also cover accessories with a value of up to &pound;100 including VAT, meaning there's no need to worry if you lose your favourite case, headset or other important accessories at the same time as your mobile device. You do your stuff, because we have your back.</p>
