{% block extra_content_two %}
    <h2 class="h3 mb-4 text-primary">We believe phone insurance should be easy, inexpensive and clear</h2>
    <p>Our Samsung Galaxy S9+ cover includes everything you need to use your handset with total confidence, from full cover for your phone to coverage for your favorite mobile accessories.</p>
    <p>In addition to our mobile device coverage, we provide cover for up to &pound;1,000 worth of network charges, meaning there's no need for you to worry after your device goes missing. We'll even cover you overseas while you're traveling the world, with up to 90 days of global coverage.</p>
    <p>Need to make a claim? We're here to help, and fast. We aim to provide a replacement or repair within 24-72 hours of approving your claim, with 74% of our claims completely settled within 24 hours or less. Moreover, our claims team in based in the UK and they're our colleagues, not strangers.</p>
    <p>Don't need to make a claim? To make your insurance as affordable as possible, we offer up to 80% of your policy as cashback if you and your connections don't make any claims throughout the year. You don't get this with other phone insurers.</p>
